episodes.title: Showdown at the Broken Spoke
episodes.plot: A honky-tonk dance instructor known for her Daisy Dukes isn't your typical grandma. Her daughter wants her to rein it in -- but change won't be easy.

episodes.title: Angel Gets Her Wings
episodes.plot: A trans powerlifter dominates in the gym but struggles with self-confidence in public. Can the Fab Five help her harness her inner strength?

episodes.title: No More Bull
episodes.plot: A rugged rancher grew up fast as one of the youngest Army Rangers in history. Now he longs for a wife and family, but his habits need serious help.

episodes.title: A Night to Remember
episodes.plot: The Fab Five help a high school prom committee deal with the stress and loss of a difficult year as they plan an outdoor dance during a pandemic.

episodes.title: Craw-Zaddy
episodes.plot: Years after his wife's passing, a quirky restaurant owner is ready for change. But both he and his old school eatery remain trapped in days gone by.

episodes.title: Community Allied
episodes.plot: When the pandemic revealed inequities in her community, a passionate health care professional took action. Now it's her turn to practice self-care.

episodes.title: Snow White of Central Texas
episodes.plot: The overworked founder of a rescue organization for special-needs animals is so busy taking care of others that she doesn't make time for herself.

episodes.title: Gimme Shelter
episodes.plot: A hardworking humanitarian with big dreams and a selfless heart steps up his style to raise money for a state-of-the-art community for the homeless.

episodes.title: A Legend in the Baking
episodes.plot: The gang gets cooking with a funky, eclectic baker who's seen hard times and needs a boost to be the face of her business again. The results are sweet.

episodes.title: The Mis-Inspiration of Reggie Devore
episodes.plot: A gifted rapper lost his passion for making music when a global pandemic put his career on pause. Can the Fab Five help him get his groove back?
